quran[44]{c,v,t}:
  70,1,Mangne waley ne azaab maanga hai (woh azaab) jo zaroor waqey honay wala hai
  70,2,"Kafiron ke liye hai, koi usey dafa karne wala nahin"
  70,3,Us khuda ki taraf se hai jo urooj ke zeeno (ascending steps)ka malik hai
  70,4,Malaika (angels) aur rooh(Jibrael) uske huzoor chadh kar jatey hain ek aise din mein jiski miqdar pacchas (fifty) hazar saal hai
  70,5,"Pas aey Nabi, sabr karo, shaista sabr"
  70,6,Yeh log usey dur samajhte hain
  70,7,Aur hum usey qareeb dekh rahey hain
  70,8,(woh azaab us roz hoga) jis roz aasman pigli huye chandi ki tarah ho jayega
  70,9,Aur pahad rang-bi-rang ke dhunke huey oon (wool) jaise ho jayenge
  70,10,Aur koi jigri dost apne jigri dost ko na puchega
  70,11,"Halaanke woh ek dusre ko dikhaye jayenge, mujrim chahega ke us din ke azaab se bachne ke liye apni aulad ko"
  70,12,"Apni biwi ko, apne bhai ko"
  70,13,Apne qareeb-tareen khandaan ko jo usey panaah dene wala tha
  70,14,Aur rooh-e-zameen ke sab logon ko fidiya (badle) mein dey-de aur yeh tadbeer usey nijaat dila de
  70,15,Hargiz nahin woh to bhadakti hui aag ki lapat hogi
  70,16,Jo gosht posht ko chaat jayegi
  70,17,Pukar pukar kar apni taraf bulayegi har us shaks ko jisne haqq se mooh moda aur peet pheri
  70,18,Aur maal jamaa kiya aur seint seint kar (amassed wealth) rakkha
  70,19,Insan thud-dila (impatient) paida kiya gaya hai
  70,20,Jab uspar museebat aati hai to ghabra uthta hai
  70,21,Aur jab usey khush-haali naseeb hoti hai to bukhl (kanjoosi) karne lagta hai
  70,22,Magar woh log (is aib se bache huey hai) jo namaz padne waley hain
  70,23,Jo apni namaz ki hamesha pabandi karte hai
  70,24,Jinke maalon mein
  70,25,Saahil (maangne waley) aur mehroom ka ek haqq mukarrar hai
  70,26,Jo roz-e-jaza ko barhaq maante hain
  70,27,Jo apne Rubb ke azaab se darte hain
  70,28,Kyunke unke Rubb ka azaab aisi cheez nahin hai jissey koi bekhauf ho
  70,29,Jo apni sharmgahon ki hifazat karte hain
  70,30,Ba-juz apne biwiyon ya apni mamluka aurton ke jinse mehfooz na rakhne mein unpar koi malamat nahin
  70,31,Albatta jo iske alawa kuch aur chahein wahi hadd se tajawuz karne wala hai
  70,32,Jo apne amanaton ki hifazat aur apne ahad (covenant) ka paas karte hai
  70,33,Jo apni gawahiyon mein raast baazi (upright) par qayam rehte hain
  70,34,Aur jo apni namaz ki hifazat karte hain
  70,35,Yeh log izzat ke saath jannat ke baaghon mei rahenge
  70,36,"Pas aey Nabi , kya baat hai ke yeh munkirin dayein(left) aur bayein(right) se"
  70,37,Giroh (crowds) dar giroh(crowds) tumhari taraf daude chale aa rahe hain
  70,38,Kya inmein se har ek yeh lalaj rakhta hai ke woh niyamat bhari jannat mein daakhil kardiya jayega
  70,39,Hargiz nahin humne jis cheez se inko paida kiya hai usey yeh khud jaante hain
  70,40,"Pas nahin, main qasam khata hoon mashrikon aur maghribon ke maalik ki hum ispar qadir hain"
  70,41,Ke inki jagah insey behtar log le aayein aur koi humse baazi le jaane wala nahin hai
  70,42,Lihaza inhein apni behuda baaton aur apne khel mein pada rehne do yahan tak ke yeh apne us din ko pahunch jayenge jiska insey waada kiya ja raha hai
  70,43,Jab yeh apni qabron se nikal kar is tarah daude ja rahey hongey jaise apne buthon (idols) ke aasthano (altars) ki taraf daud rahey hon
  70,44,"Inki nigahein jhuki hui hongi, zillat inpar chaa rahi hogi, woh din hai jiska insey wada kiya ja raha hai"